Class Cache

  • java.lang.Object
    • Cache
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FIFOCache, LFUCache, LRUCache, RandomCache
    public class Cache
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a Cache. This is the parent class of all the other caches included in the simulation.

        protected void incrementIndex()
